            . I am <rs id="t18181028-85-viclabel498" type="occupation">hostler</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-85-victim631 t18181028-85-viclabel498"></join> to a gentleman in Hertfordshire. On the 20th of October I lost my coat off my waggon, in <placeName id="t18181028-85-crimeloc499">Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18181028-85-crimeloc499" type="placeName" value="Smithfield"></interp>
